<title>中方：纯属子虚乌有，不要患上被迫害妄想症</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%AF%E5%B1%9E%E5%AD%90%E8%99%9A%E4%B9%8C%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%82%A3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E5%AE%B3%E5%A6%84%E6%83%B3%E7%97%87</link>
